dct_title_s: County and railroad map of New York
dct_alternative_sm: Rand, McNally & Co.'s county and railroad map of New York
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich Meridian.

"This map, with index, by which counties, cities, railroads, lakes, rivers, etc, can be located as readily as a word can be found in a dictionary ; with population, names of express companies, etc ; neatly bound."
Topographic map with contour lines. Includes an inset map of Long Island.
Pocket-size folding map showing topography, rivers, railroads, towns, and counties.
Index map on verso: Rand, McNally & Co.'s New indexed pocket maps.
